---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Base
  title="KYDE Labs — KYDE"
  description="Where we push the boundary of what governed AI agents can do. KYDE Labs explores what becomes possible when AI agents operate with verifiable trust — in the physical world, at scale."
>
  <Navbar />

  <main>

    <!-- ══════════ HERO ══════════ -->
    <section class="relative overflow-hidden pt-36 pb-24 md:pt-48 md:pb-36">
      <div class="bg-grid absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="pointer-events-none absolute top-0 left-0 h-[500px] w-[700px] rounded-full bg-blue-600/5 blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="pointer-events-none absolute bottom-0 right-0 h-[400px] w-[500px] rounded-full bg-cyan-600/5 blur-3xl"></div>

      <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <p class="mb-6 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-blue-400">KYDE Labs</p>
        <h1 class="max-w-3xl text-5xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight text-white md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
          Where we push the boundary of what governed AI agents can do.
        </h1>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ══════════ WHAT IS LABS ══════════ -->
    <section class="relative py-24 md:py-32">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black via-zinc-900/30 to-black pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_2fr]">

          <div>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-blue-400">The Lab</p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-zinc-300">
            <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">
              KYDE Labs explores what becomes possible when AI agents operate with verifiable trust — in the physical world, at scale.
            </p>
            <p>
              Silicon Leash solves the governance problem for AI agents in enterprise software. Labs asks the next question: what happens when those same agents step outside the browser and into physical systems?
            </p>
            <p class="text-zinc-400">
              Energy grids. Industrial infrastructure. Autonomous hardware. Environments where a bad decision doesn't produce a wrong document — it trips a breaker, misallocates storage capacity, or causes a grid imbalance at 2am.
            </p>
            <p>
              The audit requirements are higher. The stakes are higher. The governance layer has to be deeper.
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ══════════ FIRST USE CASE ══════════ -->
    <section class="py-24 md:py-32">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">

        <div class="max-w-2xl mb-12">
          <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-blue-400">First Published Use Case</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">AI agent governance for energy infrastructure and battery management systems.</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3 max-w-4xl">

          <div class="rounded-sm border border-emerald-400/20 bg-zinc-900/60 p-8">
            <div class="mb-4 h-8 w-8 rounded-sm border border-emerald-400/20 bg-emerald-400/5 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-emerald-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 13.5l10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-mono text-base font-bold text-white mb-2">Energy Infrastructure</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">AI agents managing load balancing, grid dispatch, and operational decisions — with every action signed, timestamped, and verifiable.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-sm border border-cyan-400/20 bg-zinc-900/60 p-8">
            <div class="mb-4 h-8 w-8 rounded-sm border border-cyan-400/20 bg-cyan-400/5 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-cyan-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 10.5h.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v2.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125H21M4.5 10.5H18V15H4.5v-4.5zM3.75 18h15A2.25 2.25 0 0021 15.75v-6a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25h-15A2.25 2.25 0 001.5 9.75v6A2.25 2.25 0 003.75 18z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-mono text-base font-bold text-white mb-2">Battery Management</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">Automated charge/discharge decisions in large-scale battery storage — governed by the same tamper-evident append-only database that runs in enterprise software stacks.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-sm border border-blue-400/20 bg-zinc-900/60 p-8">
            <div class="mb-4 h-8 w-8 rounded-sm border border-blue-400/20 bg-blue-400/5 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-mono text-base font-bold text-white mb-2">NIS-2 & KRITIS Ready</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">Physical infrastructure is in scope for NIS-2 and Germany's KRITIS regulation. Labs builds the governance layer before enforcement begins.</p>
          </div>

        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ══════════ COMING SOON ══════════ -->
    <section class="py-24 md:py-32">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="rounded-sm border border-zinc-700 bg-zinc-900/40 p-12 md:p-16 max-w-2xl">

          <div class="mb-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-blue-400/20 bg-blue-400/5 px-3 py-1">
            <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-400 animate-pulse"></span>
            <span class="text-xs font-medium text-blue-400">Coming soon</span>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">
            Research, write-ups, and early results will be published here.
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed">
            If you're building at the intersection of AI agents and physical infrastructure — energy, grid tech, industrial automation — we want to hear from you.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-8">
            <a
              href="mailto:hello@kyde.com"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-sm border border-zinc-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-200 hover:border-zinc-400 hover:text-white transition-all"
            >
              hello@kyde.com →
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

  <Footer />
</Base>
